caption: The North Dakota State Capitol building, a gray silhouette against a black background, displays the words "NORTH" and "Dakota" in white, accompanied by the phrase "Be Legendary.".  The image features a logo for North Dakota. The logo consists of the word "NORTH" written in a large, bold font above the word "Dakota." The text is in a dark gray color against a black background. Below the logo, there is a line of text that says "Be Legendary." The overall design is simple and straightforward, with a focus on the North Dakota state name.

A group of people in business attire collaborate on a wooden desk, using laptops, phones, and a coffee cup, with a view of a city skyline..  The image shows a group of people standing together with their fists clenched, forming a circle. They are gathered around a wooden table, which has several laptops, a cell phone, a cup, and a notebook. The laptops are open and appear to be in use. The people are wearing business attire, and there are various cords and cables visible on the table. A cell phone is placed on the table, and a cup is located near the right edge of the image. A notebook is also present on the table.
